item.title: CVE-2016-9991|2024-08-06T03:07:31.857Z -- ibm -- sterling%20order%20management
item.description: IBM Sterling Order Management 9.2 through 9.5 is vulnerable to cross-site request forgery which could allow an attacker to execute malicious and unauthorized actions transmitted from a user that the website trusts. IBM X-Force ID: 121314.
